{"title":"CentOS中Rsync加入自动启动服务","uid":"381f6f7e3cde6d1b00fec638aae91387","slug":"linux/CentOS中Rsync加入自动启动服务","date":"2024-03-16T11:44:51.808Z","updated":"2024-03-16T11:44:51.809Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/linux/CentOS中Rsync加入自动启动服务.json","keywords":"AIGC,LLM,糖果AIGC实验室","cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"centos中rsync加入自动启动服务\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#centos中rsync加入自动启动服务\"></a> CentOS中Rsync加入自动启动服务</h1>\n<p>在CentOS下，如何将rsync服务，加入到systemctl自动启动项目中，如何进行配置</p>\n<p>要将rsync服务加入到systemctl自动启动项目中，在CentOS下，可以按照以下步骤进行配置：</p>\n<ol>\n<li class=\"lvl-3\">\n<p>创建一个rsync的systemd服务配置文件。在终端中执行以下命令：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo nano /etc/systemd/system/rsync.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li class=\"lvl-3\">\n<p>在打开的文件中，输入以下内容：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[Unit]</span><br><span class=\"line\">Description=rsync service</span><br><span class=\"line\">After=network.target</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[Service]</span><br><span class=\"line\">ExecStart=/usr/bin/rsync --daemon --config=/etc/rsyncd.conf</span><br><span class=\"line\">Restart=always</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[Install]</span><br><span class=\"line\">WantedBy=default.target</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li class=\"lvl-3\">\n<p>保存并关闭文件。</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"lvl-3\">\n<p>创建一个rsync的配置文件。在终端中执行以下命令：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo nano /etc/rsyncd.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li class=\"lvl-3\">\n<p>在打开的文件中，输入你想要的rsync配置。例如，下面是一个简单的示例：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">uid = nobody</span><br><span class=\"line\">gid = nobody</span><br><span class=\"line\">use chroot = yes</span><br><span class=\"line\">max connections = 4</span><br><span class=\"line\">strict modes = yes</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[myshare]</span><br><span class=\"line\">path = /path/to/your/folder</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment = My shared folder</span><br><span class=\"line\">read only = no</span><br><span class=\"line\">list = yes </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li class=\"lvl-3\">\n<p>保存并关闭文件。</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"lvl-3\">\n<p>启动并激活rsync服务。在终端中执行以下命令：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo systemctl start rsync.service</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo systemctl enable rsync.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>现在，每次系统启动时，rsync服务都会自动启动。</p>\n","text":" CentOS中Rsync加入自动启动服务 在CentOS下，如何将rsync服务，加入到systemctl自动启动